Who we are

CambodiaTrade is an e-commerce marketplace, located at CambodiaTrade.com, operated by the Ministry of Commerce of Cambodia to serve Cambodiaâ€™s small and medium enterprises to sell their products online to potential clients in the domestic and cross-border markets. The marketplace is developed with financial support from the Enhanced Integrated Framework under the Go4eCAM project with the main objective in realizing the benefits of e-commerce for the SMEs.

Our vision

Our primary vision of having the CambodiaTrade B2B2C marketplace platform is to increase economic opportunities for Cambodian SMEs to participate in both domestic or cross-border E-commerce and Digital Economy.

Our mission

To develop business environment for e-commerce firms through a highly visible national B2B2C e-marketplace with fully integrated payment gateways and logistic solutions, and adhering to international standards and best regulatory practices, operated by the Ministry of Commerce for Cambodian urban and provincial businesses targeting both domestic and cross-border e-commerce.
